Find the value of the constant $c_1$ in the steady state solution $u(x) = c_1 - 2x$ for the following PDE problem:
\begin{align}
u_{t} &= u_{xx} \\
u_{x}(t,0) &= u_{x}(t,4) = -2 \\
u(0,x) &= \begin{cases} 0 & 0 \leq x \leq 2 \\ 2x-4 & 2 \leq x \leq 4 \end{cases}
\end{align}
Choose $c_1$ such that the total heat energy as $t \rightarrow \infty$ is the same as when $t=0$.}

