\[t = \frac{1}{AC} + \frac{1}{BC}\]is a fixed constant.  Find the constant $t.$

[asy]
unitsize(1 cm);

real parab (real x) {
  return(x^2);
}

pair A, B, C;

A = (1.7,parab(1.7));
B = (-1,parab(-1));
